{"id": 2961, "genre": 1001, "title": "你心目中的理想工作状态是怎样的？", "description": "什么样工作状态，会让你谈及自己的工作时，更愿意把它作为自己的一部分，而不是用“我只是给别人打工的”来描述你的工作。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA Printstock）", "record_count": 2433, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190521210550psq27f1eXEJKISht.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-05-27T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 345856, "content": "确确实实，完完全全，百分百是自己欣然接受的活动，接近于一项兴趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434723}, {"id": 347392, "content": "为啥日报又回到过去啦！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 959110}, {"id": 345857, "content": "能往自己想要的方向发展，公司的政策和我的想法吻合", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1494482}, {"id": 345858, "content": "有一个懂你的领导.", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1657669}, {"id": 345861, "content": "可以在家做的创意自由职业 画画 写写字 出出设计都很好  平常再去我的奶茶店巡逻一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531223}, {"id": 345862, "content": "做的工作是走向觉悟", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1203883}, {"id": 345863, "content": "让我愿意从早上睁眼到晚上闭眼都一直在做一直在想的工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1657776}, {"id": 345864, "content": "一天比一天有进步和出成绩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1657778}, {"id": 345865, "content": "和志同道合的小伙伴们一起做自己热爱的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1657791}, {"id": 345866, "content": "工作不只是一份赚钱的工具，还能从中获得成就感，提高自身能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1653250}, {"id": 345611, "content": "不要996", "image": null, "praise_count": 83, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 813793}, {"id": 345867, "content": "做五休二，上下级尽可能对等，做自己喜欢的事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1642332}, {"id": 345612, "content": "工作是自驱，而不是被强迫", "image": null, "praise_count": 198, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1376859}, {"id": 345868, "content": "一天结束后，不会觉得是虚度", "image": "img/option/option/20190828092314XQSxVRpAeZ27wEnl", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1657897}, {"id": 345613, "content": "罢了罢了", "image": "img/option/option/201905271104528tsqVgpHW6hBwK2i", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407519}, {"id": 345869, "content": "50%日常，50%挑战，完成度在95%，有成就感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1657903}, {"id": 348941, "content": "个人价值可以被尊重并实现", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557069}, {"id": 345614, "content": "专注，不浮于表面，有持续产出，有持续进步", "image": null, "praise_count": 118, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1656926}, {"id": 346382, "content": "我选择了以此为生，并甘苦如饴", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802061}, {"id": 345615, "content": "做二休五", "image": null, "praise_count": 240, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525473}, {"id": 345616, "content": "我的理想是不工作还有钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1656929}, {"id": 345872, "content": "目前自己的工作状态就比较满意，上一周休息三周。在家工作，压力中等。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202429}, {"id": 345617, "content": "有共同的信任。有共同的信任，才能在一起做事，完成同一个目标", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605775}, {"id": 345618, "content": "只要薪资够，谁管996？", "image": "img/option/option/20190527111635csrnST7g8bXuQvaV.jpg", "praise_count": 100, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500430}, {"id": 345874, "content": "有创造的部分，有机械重复的部分，具体可以根据个人状态安排", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1652353}, {"id": 345619, "content": "能像电视剧里那样吗？想上班就上班，上班还可以聊八卦，环境还很好", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 391490}, {"id": 345875, "content": "创造价值，按时睡觉，得到理解。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540498}, {"id": 345620, "content": "只要每天不是一层不变的机械运动，有社交有能力突破有情感收获，逐步达成人生节点目标。", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1656933}, {"id": 345876, "content": "有成就感，并且有足够空余时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 345621, "content": "工作是自己的兴趣爱好或者特长", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1580833}, {"id": 345877, "content": "公司是一个的自由言论的聚集地，想法跟行动力的碰撞，没上级的工作分配，只有统筹结合的觥筹交错", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198853}, {"id": 345622, "content": "在一个优秀的机构，拥有改变该机构不好的地方的能量，能够做出决策，钱只要够用，达到中等水平就行，还要有福利", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623175}, {"id": 345878, "content": "想离职", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 739709}, {"id": 345623, "content": "时间自己安排，工作地点自己安排", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224481}, {"id": 345879, "content": "成就感", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883272}, {"id": 345880, "content": "没有固定工作时间，友善的伙伴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1658051}, {"id": 345625, "content": "轻松，每天上班都是开心的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 345626, "content": "有一定发挥空间，有持续的进步，融洽积极的团队氛围，有富余的时间掌控自己的兴趣和副业", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629931}, {"id": 345882, "content": "没有猪一样的队友，只有跟我一样的人才", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619703}, {"id": 345627, "content": "睡着的时候钱也可以往钱包里走", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473725}, {"id": 345883, "content": "靠自己的大脑和行动做出被他人肯定的产出。如果在这个基础上，有闲有钱，就更好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003826}, {"id": 345885, "content": "成就感", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179186}, {"id": 345630, "content": "可以一成不变，但每天都要有一点不同的挑战性，可以繁杂多样，但能实现个人价值", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1656941}, {"id": 345886, "content": "对公司和自己都充满认同感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066159}, {"id": 345887, "content": "工作的真实", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1658175}, {"id": 345888, "content": "能够带来成就感，并能够产生积累和持续成长", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1021047}, {"id": 345889, "content": "脚踏实地的帮助到别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1658212}, {"id": 345634, "content": "坐4休3 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609349}, {"id": 345890, "content": "不再为生计出卖时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 15234}, {"id": 347426, "content": "和一些情商高，有拼劲，对自己又有要求的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547590}]}